This turned out to be the improperly constructed query: you need to use "query" before "filter" - it does matter!
The query should look like:
```json
{
  "query": {
    "filtered": {
      "query": {"match": {"search_key": "my_key_value"}},
      "filter": { "term": {"applicationType":"myapptype"} }
      
    },
    "aggs": {"client": {"terms": {"field": "client"}}},
    "size": 0
  }
}
```
And everything works then.

